About The Fifth Label

The Fifth Label is a contemporary Vietnamese fashion brand dedicated to the new generation of trendsetters. We are inspired by the bold spirit and creativity of youth — those who are not afraid to stand out, break boundaries, and express their individuality through style.

At The Fifth Label, we believe fashion should be more than just wearable — it should be expressive, effortless, and empowering. Our collections are carefully curated to reflect a balance of minimalism and character, offering versatile pieces that seamlessly adapt to every moment in your day-to-day life.

From chic crop tops and structured blazers, to flowing maxi dresses and signature skirts, each item is designed with attention to detail, high-quality materials, and affordable prices — making modern fashion accessible without compromise.

Whether you're dressing for a casual hangout, a night out, or simply expressing your everyday mood, The Fifth Label is here to help you define your style story — one look at a time.

Join our journey. Dress with confidence. Express yourself.
The Fifth Label – Where fashion meets identity.
